rows.label: qst200703_0010
rows.name:
Oh ho ho!
Mushrooms all for me!

rows.label: qst200703_0020
rows.name: He looks so happy.

rows.label: qst200703_0030
rows.name: He must really like mushrooms.

rows.label: qst200703_0040
rows.name:
Stop mushroom talk... Tora not want to see another
as long as Tora live... *burp* 'Scuse me...

rows.label: qst200703_0050
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: qst200703_0060
rows.name: What in God's name are you doing, Idaten?

rows.label: qst200703_0070
rows.name: Looking for something?

rows.label: qst200703_0080
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: qst200703_0090
rows.name: What is this?

rows.label: qst200703_0100
rows.name: What did you find? ...Idaten?

rows.label: qst200703_0110
rows.name: What's that card?

rows.label: qst200703_0120
rows.name: Uhhh...

rows.label: qst200703_0130
rows.name:
"Thanks for the food!"
From...Yumyum the Burglar?

rows.label: qst200703_0140
rows.name:
Huh... Is this...
Is this a message from the thief?

rows.label: qst200703_0150
rows.name: Whuh?!

rows.label: qst200703_0160
rows.name:
Looks like he snuck in while we were away and
nicked all of our food.

rows.label: qst200703_0170
rows.name: No no no no no!

rows.label: qst200703_0180
rows.name: Calm down, Idaten!

rows.label: qst200703_0190
rows.name: This is unacceptable. Unacceptable!

rows.label: qst200703_0200
rows.name: Meh meh?!

rows.label: qst200703_0210
rows.name: Meeeeh-eh?!

rows.label: qst200703_0220
rows.name: You disappeared for a second there, Idaten.

rows.label: qst200703_0230
rows.name: ...Did you...uh...go somewhere and come back just now?

rows.label: qst200703_0240
rows.name: I didn't go anywhere!

rows.label: qst200703_0250
rows.name: What's that, then?

rows.label: qst200703_0260
rows.name: This? This undelicious-looking piece of...of nothing?

rows.label: qst200703_0270
rows.name:
You were carrying that when you came in.
You don't know where you got it from?

rows.label: qst200703_0280
rows.name:
I was so angry that I lost track of everything!
I have no idea where this came from!

rows.label: qst200703_0290
rows.name:
Analysis indicate that carving is not
from Avaritia.

rows.label: qst200703_0300
rows.name: So Idaten traveled to another country in that split second?

rows.label: qst200703_0310
rows.name:
I knew the blighter was fast,
but I didn't think he was THAT fast.

rows.label: qst200703_0320
rows.name:
We should try to return that carving before
its owner notices it's gone.

rows.label: qst200703_0330
rows.name:
He's right.
But looking for the owner sounds like a right hassle.

rows.label: qst200703_0340
rows.name:
Perhaps by studying the statue, we'll be able
to discern its origin.
